data.title: Student Awards, Competitions & Recognition | College of Science
data.meta_description: Learna about student competitions, awards and the Dean's List at the College of Science at the University of Nevada, Reno.
data.text:
In order to make the College of Science Dean's List, a student must have completed at least 12 units of graded coursework during the semester and have received a 3.75 semester GPA.

NOTE: Only the names of students who qualified for the Spring 2024 College of Science Dean's List and have given directory release permission have been published on the College of Science website.
